    <label>macro-ant</label>
    <description>"I knew an ant once, but she wouldn't admit it. Also, I've always wondered if you can tattoo an ant." \n \n The macro-ant is a type of massive ant, which is about the same size as a Megascarab, but far weaker. Like its fellow Insectoids, which it will often be found near, it was engineered to wage war against the Mechanoids in ages long past. Being the weakest of the standard Insectoids, it was mainly deployed as cannon fodder to distract Mechanoids, or was bred for its meat. \n \n Ants are eusocial insects, all classified under the taxonomic family &lt;i>Formicidae&lt;/i>.</description>
